Package it.polimi.travlendarplus.RESTful.messages.authenticationMessages

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthenticationMessage
    Main authentication message class, to be extended by all messages used to authenticate the users.
    AuthenticationResponse
    Main authentication message response class, to be extended by all messages used to reply to the user after an authentication request.
    Credentials
    Message to be sent by a client to perform a login
    EmailMessage
    Message sent when the user want to reset his password and he have to specify his email
    LoginResponse
    Response message used to reply to the users after a login operation
    PublicKeyResponse
    Response message used to reply to the users after an public key request with the public key associated with the device the request come from.
    RegistrationForm
    Message sent when an user want to register himself into the system or when he wants to modify his profile
    TokenResponse
    Response message used to reply to the users after an authentication-related request with the univocal code associated with the device the request come from.
